  (506,165,108,'a:1:{i:8;s:449:\"With the cooperation of Qulix QA specialists we have effectively deployed an end-to-end solution IBM Rational in order to run automated functional and load testing for a large-scale industrial enterprise in Russia. &nbsp;SM-Consult together with Qulix initiated the development and implementation of methodology and technology for automated functional testing and provided training programs for in-house staff. Thank you for much-needed expert help!\";}'),
