  (511,166,108,'a:1:{i:8;s:359:\"Our cooperation with Qulix QA teachers has now continued for four years. Their discipline, high-level training and creative approach in terms of communication with course participants are well worth respect. Special thanks for the development and non-stop improvement of efficient training programs that enjoy immense popularity and receive excellent reviews.\";}'),
