  (516,167,108,'a:1:{i:8;s:374:\"Independent quality assurance is of critical importance for successful implementation of integrated systems, developed by our company. We have had several years of close cooperation with Qulix QA in the QA and independent expert software testing domains. This cooperation makes us believe that we deliver reliable software products of premium quality to our customers.<br />\";}'),
