  (521,168,108,'a:1:{i:8;s:286:\"I was impressed with your attitude, guys. Feedback to my requests was received immediately and it was really easy for me to supervise the project from start to finalization. It is the first time I have had successful experience of speaking a common language with an offshore team.<br />\";}'),
