  (526,169,108,'a:1:{i:8;s:309:\"Qulix QA has become a reliable partner for our company. Qualified specialists, prompt responses to enquiries, and transparent project management are what we expected to get and what we actually got as a result of our joint activity. We&amp;rsquo;ll be glad to go through this experience of success once again.\";}'),
